Another slide map.
My first REAL slide map but still in beta

Slide_miningcaves was just a practice

Here is a long fun and challenging slide map, just like sliderace_city, with a winter theme and a reward at the end.

Includes
-dying when hit walls
-gun room at end
-extra cource to play if your up for it
-teleports back to spawn for doing the map over if you finished
-falling spikes

more to come...

Enjoy,
                 Disturbed
